      <h2>About Us</h2>
      <p><strong>YOU DECIDE</strong> is a graphic design company that connects talented designers with clients from different domains and industries who require graphic design services for various projects. Whether you need a logo, a flyer, a poster, a brochure, or any other graphic design work, we can help you find the best designer for your needs and budget.</p>

      <p>Our company was founded by <strong>Arsalan Rahman</strong>, a passionate graphic designer who started his career as a freelancer and worked with many clients from different fields. He realized that there was a gap in the market for a platform that could match clients with designers based on their specific requirements and preferences. He decided to create <strong>YOU DECIDE</strong>, a company that empowers both clients and designers to make their own decisions and collaborate effectively.</p>

      <p>Since its inception, <strong>YOU DECIDE</strong> has grown rapidly and has become one of the leading graphic design companies in the country. We have a network of over 500 designers who specialize in various styles and niches. We have served over 10,000 clients from different sectors, such as education, health, entertainment, tourism, and more. We have generated over $5 million in revenue per year and have received many awards and recognitions for our work.</p>
